[[File:Exoplanet_Comparison_CoRoT-7_b.png|右]]和[[海王星|海王星]]相比，推斷的超級地球[[柯洛7b|柯洛7b]]（中間）大小的圖示]]
'''超级地球'''是太阳系外行星，其质量高于[[地球|地球]]，但远低于[[天王星|天王星]]和[[海王星|海王星]]一類的太阳系[[冰巨行星|冰巨星]]，后者分别是地球的14.5和17倍。它仅是指行星的质量，并不意味着有关表面状况或[[行星適居性|可居住性]]。<ref name="Valencia">{{cite journal |language=en
 |last=Valencia |first=V.
 |last2=Sasselov |first2=D. D.
 |last3=O'Connell |first3=R. J.
 |year=2007
 |title=Radius and structure models of the first super-earth planet
 |url=http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/0004-637X/656/1/545/65923.html
 |journal=[[天文物理期刊|The Astrophysical Journal]]
 |volume=656 |issue=1 |pages=545–551
 |arxiv=astro-ph/0610122
 |bibcode=2007ApJ...656..545V
 |doi=10.1086/509800
}}</ref>自从2005年[[格利泽876d|格利泽876d]]被[[尤金尼亞·里維拉|尤金尼亞·里維拉]]（Eugenio Rivera）所率领的团队发现之后，相继有数颗超级地球被世人发现。[[地球|地球]]作为太阳系中最大的[[类地行星|类地行星]]，其所身处的[[太阳系|太阳系]]并不包含这一类能被当作范例的行星，举凡那些体积大过地球的行星，质量至少都在其十倍以上。

== 定義 ==
[[File:Artist’s_impression_of_the_super-Earth_exoplanet_LHS_1140b.jpg|缩略图]]的印象。]]
在一般情況下，超級地球只以[[質量|質量]]作為判定條件，而[[溫度|溫度]]、組合成分、軌道屬性、適居性、或星球環境等條件則不包括在內。目前在超級地球質量上限定義上，普遍認同為地球質量的10倍<ref name="Valencia"/><ref name="Fortney">{{cite journal |language=en
 |last=Fortney |first=J. J.
 |last2=Marley |first2=M. S.
 |last3=Barnes |first3=J. W.
 |year=2007
 |title=Planetary Radii across Five Orders of Magnitude in Mass and Stellar Insolation: Application to Transits
 |url=http://iopscience.iop.org/0004-637X/659/2/1661/fulltext/
 |journal=The [[天文物理期刊|Astrophysical Journal]]
 |volume=659 |issue=2 |pages=1661–1672
 |arxiv=astro-ph/0612671
 |bibcode=2007ApJ...659.1661F
 |doi=10.1086/512120
}}</ref><ref name="Charbonneau-GJ1214b"> {{cite journal |language=en
 |last1=Charbonneau |first1=D.
 |author2=et al.
 |year=2009
 |title=A super-Earth transiting a nearby low-mass star
 |journal=[[自然_(期刊)|Nature]]
 |volume=462 |pages=891–894
 |arxiv= 0912.3229
 |bibcode = 2009Natur.462..891C
 |doi=10.1038/nature08679
 |pmid=20016595
 |issue=7275
}}</ref>（約[[天王星|天王星]]質量的69%，這是太陽系的氣體巨型最小的質量），而下限為地球質量的1倍<ref name="Valencia"/>、1.9倍<ref name="Charbonneau-GJ1214b"/>、5倍<ref name="Fortney"/>不等，在不同的大眾媒體下有不同的標準。<ref>{{cite web
 |language    = en
 |last        = Spotts
 |first       = P. N.
 |date        = 2007-04-28
 |url         = https://www.thespec.com/news-story/2157544-canada-s-orbiting-telescope-tracks-mystery-super-earth-/
 |title       = Canada's orbiting telescope tracks mystery 'super Earth'
 |work        = The Hamilton Spectator
 |accessdate  = 2012-04-28
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20151107063640/http://www.thespec.com/news-story/2157544-canada-s-orbiting-telescope-tracks-mystery-super-earth-/
 |archivedate = 2015-11-07
}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |language=en
 |date         = 2007-11-11
 |title        = Life could survive longer on a super-Earth
 |url          = http://space.newscientist.com/article/mg19626295.300-life-could-survive-longer-on-a-superearth.html
 |work         = [[新科學人|New Scientist]]
